values: ATTENTION FRIENDS LIST!!! (and anyone else) I have a new livejournal!!! I've already added all of you onto my list, if you add me back that would be great. I'm reaching the one-year anniversary of this livejournal and i frankly dont like the name anymore. so I'm starting fresh...but i'm not deleting this. there's too many memories and things. au revoir, old name.
if you wanna, i might... be friends. comment, kids.
